15786: # 📚 Database Documentation — VTC HUB (Supabase)
15787: 
15788: ## 🧠 Overview
15789: 
15790: Base de données d’un ERP SaaS multi-tenant pour chauffeurs VTC.
15791: 
15792: Principes :
15793: 
15794: - Multi-tenant strict
15795: - Isolation via `tenant_id`
15796: - Auth séparée (`auth.users`)
15797: - Activation transactionnelle (`approve_onboarding_tx`)
15798: - RLS activé sur tables métier
15799: - Contraintes SQL garantissant l’intégrité métier
15800: 
15801: ---
15802: 
15803: # 🏢 Multi-Tenant Architecture
15804: 
15805: Chaque entreprise = 1 `tenant`.
15806: 
15807: Isolation garantie par :
15808: 
15809: ```
15810: tenant_id uuid
15811: ```
15812: 
15813: Tables liées au tenant (V1 actif) :
15814: 
15815: - drivers
15816: - vehicles
15817: - pricing_rules
15818: - bookings
15819: 
15820: ---
15821: 
15822: # 🔐 Auth Flow
15823: 
15824: ```
15825: auth.users
15826:    ↓ (trigger)
15827: profiles
15828:    ↓
15829: onboarding (staging)
15830:    ↓
15831: approve_onboarding_tx()
15832:    ↓
15833: tenants + drivers + vehicles + pricing_rules
15834: ```
